Last Broadcast Date: Mon 12 Sep 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, Paul and Rachel Chandler tell how they were held hostage in Somalia for over a year after being kidnapped from their yacht. And, we hear from the Somali-born businessman who worked for six months and risked his life to secure their release. Show less